Executive Profile
B. Allen Lay  Chairman of the Board, Chief Executive Officer and President, Westbrae Natural, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships82--
Background

		Mr. B. Allen Lay has been the Chairman of Westbrae Natural, Inc. (a/k/a Vestro Natural Foods Inc.) since August 6, 1996 and as its President and Chief Executive Officer since January 12, 1995. Mr. Lay served as a General Partner of Southern California Ventures from May 1983 to 2001. He served as the Chairman and the Chief Executive Officer of Meridian Data Inc. from July 1993 to December 1994. He has been a Director of ViaSat Inc. since 1996; Kofax, Inc. (also known ... as Kofax Image Products, Inc.) since 1990 and Westbrae Natural, Inc. since 1987. He serves as a Director of Physical Optics Corporation, Waveband Corporation, Exiqon Diagnostics, Inc., Dolphin Search, Kofax Imaging Corporation, Helisys and Medclone Inc. He served as a Director of PairGain Technologies (formerly PairGain Technology, Inc.) since February 1989.Read Full Background




