Insider Activity


Individual




B. Allen Lay



Mr. B. A. Lay is Independent Director at ViaSat, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at ViaSat, Inc. 
Mr. Lay was previously employed as General Partner by Southern California Ventures. He also served on the board at Carley Lamps LLC, Luminit LLC, NPI LLC, Oncotech, Inc. and Physical Optics Corp.



